node.text: Gutted.. Puncture with 5 laps to go while running in P9 so we had to do an extra stop😑 Big shame, as I felt we deserved better after a difficult weekend for us. Quite a lot to go through now, and try to come back with more pace in Budapest. Glad to see @maxverstappen1 is ok after such a scary crash.. Thanks to all the crowd who came at the track, it was wild & amazing all weekend.❤️🇬🇧

node.text: We fought hard today.⚔️ It wasn’t an easy one starting on the soft but we tried our best. P9, and only 4secs from the Top 5, so there are some positives. We will keep working on these small details to do even better in the coming races. The fight continues.
